{"members":[{"header_text":" 193 - قَالَ: وَ أَخْرَجَ اَلْبُخَارِيُّ أَنَّهَا قَالَتْ:","body_text":"اَ تَرِثُ اَبَاكَ وَ لاَ اَرِثُ اَبِي؟ اَيْنَ اَنْتَ مِنْ قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَي: <quranic_text>«وَ وَرِثَ سُلَيْمٰانُ دٰاوُدَ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[النمل۱۶]</footnote> وَ قَوْلُهُ فِي زَكَرِيَّا: <quranic_text>«يَرِثُنِي وَ يَرِثُ مِنْ الِ يَعْقُوبَ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[مريم۶]</footnote> .","translation":"","aligned_body":"اَ تَرِثُ اَبَاكَ وَ لاَ اَرِثُ اَبِي اَيْنَ اَنْتَ مِنْ قَوْلِهِ تَعَالَي TAG_OPEN:quranic_text وَ وَرِثَ سُلَيْمٰانُ دٰاوُدَ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote النمل ۱۶ TAG_CLOSE:footnote وَ قَوْلُهُ فِي زَكَرِيَّا TAG_OPEN:quranic_text يَرِثُنِي وَ يَرِثُ مِنْ الِ يَعْقُوبَ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote مريم ۶ TAG_CLOSE:footnote"}],"body_consensus_columns":[{"kind":"word","token":"ا","display":"اَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"ترث","display":"تَرِثُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"اباك","display":"اَبَاكَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"لا","display":"لاَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"ارث","display":"اَرِثُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"ابي","display":"اَبِي"},{"kind":"word","token":"اين","display":"اَيْنَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"انت","display":"اَنْتَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"من","display":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قوله","display":"قَوْلِهِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"تعالي","display":"تَعَالَي"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"ورث","display":"وَرِثَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"سليمان","display":"سُلَيْمٰانُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"داود","display":"دٰاوُدَ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"النمل","display":"النمل"},{"kind":"word","token":"۱۶","display":"۱۶"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قوله","display":"قَوْلُهُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"في","display":"فِي"